  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>낱장인쇄물</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-83c98a35-0536-4aa2-a1d9-a699018085ad\" style=\"color:#555555;\">에 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-51feff04-b2f8-49c7-b842-c5e644d379e7\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>최선</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-692ce30c-2921-42db-ab01-1b378e67c8bb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">을 다하는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-14b9338f-0c94-470d-a647-163c06ce5b64\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-14b9338f-0c94-470d-a647-163c06ce5b64\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDNfMjcx/MDAxNzU0MjE2MjQwMzkw._gtW1jISCobm-KIi3C1d9zF-KXT8XBlsvF4NEAZ36NQg.32QOq7RQwo-dWlR7ctPWv2iV2atsO9lxm4o-mey4vOYg.PNG/%EB%9D%A0%EC%A7%80_%EC%8D%B8%EB%84%A4%EC%9D%BC001.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"595\", \"originalHeight\" : \"595\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDNfMjcx/MDAxNzU0MjE2MjQwMzkw._gtW1jISCobm-KIi3C1d9zF-KXT8XBlsvF4NEAZ36NQg.32QOq7RQwo-dWlR7ctPWv2iV2atsO9lxm4o-mey4vOYg.PNG/%EB%9D%A0%EC%A7%80_%EC%8D%B8%EB%84%A4%EC%9D%BC001.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7350edcb-30cb-4bbd-ab87-5a1f99926fb7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8abbcd6-6939-49d5-9eb7-725d2a5e290c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-91b45a36-9c5d-4d71-af05-ceaf22deb1c6\" style=\"\">띠지? 슬리브? 슬라이드?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dff02985-e4f6-4c80-864d-f30918e1f253\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ea0cb2d-55d4-4aa9-9bc7-ea9ea3e13043\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8021d151-4f11-40a7-a9f6-7d90fb4da7ed\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄물 중에는 용어가 정확하게 정의되지 않은 경우도 많습니다. 일본에서 넘어온 용어도 많을 뿐 아니라 새로운 품목이 생겨나는 경우도 있어서 용어가 통일이 되어 있지 않는 경우도 적지 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5d309c9f-c50d-4eff-b2ab-b835ff531da4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-570c1308-8a10-4b18-a117-662c02d5b945\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3fc632c8-40e0-476e-ba0e-8537a290af6d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-09c3a7e5-a063-4930-bd25-98d48c703af0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">우리가 흔히 말하는 띠지는 손목 띠지를 말합니다. 손목 띠지는 입장권을 대신해서 부착하는 용도로 많이 사용됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-34d50361-7d9a-4480-ae64-38b5e08360cd\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-34d50361-7d9a-4480-ae64-38b5e08360cd\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDNfNDQg/MDAxNzU0MjE2NTE1OTI5.lbxANVaKR6cYmjt0sKRBUdkGEq209_-0OxtUlRbHliQg.jYyGTIpVMUGkNhP39ZFXVQbJUhKJ5BPIyPnlc9lxyvUg.PNG/SE-34d50361-7d9a-4480-ae64-38b5e08360cd.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2549\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1443\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDNfNDQg/MDAxNzU0MjE2NTE1OTI5.lbxANVaKR6cYmjt0sKRBUdkGEq209_-0OxtUlRbHliQg.jYyGTIpVMUGkNhP39ZFXVQbJUhKJ5BPIyPnlc9lxyvUg.PNG/SE-34d50361-7d9a-4480-ae64-38b5e08360cd.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5770141c-19cb-452b-86bf-8fde563a437e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-19d43ac0-eccd-48ae-96f7-9607dad2fd18\" style=\"\">손목 띠지</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-47635df6-9c4a-4f73-ba65-8ae9af787fee\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1e7ae213-b9bc-47e6-9a02-13c4d4431778\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e2090001-78ef-484b-aec9-0ab40d0b95e9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 감싸는 용도로는 트레이나 프라이 팬 등을 포장하는 용도로 사용되는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0573d7ad-4379-4430-baab-d5231a0347fe\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>띠지</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2b823736-19f5-409a-8c6e-31f86ba77b72\" style=\"color:#555555;\">도 있습니다. 이런 띠지를 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cab5f29a-e491-43b8-a728-dcf1c83759aa\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>슬리브</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-02f54f85-16fd-4cb1-afe7-431cfe320c83\" style=\"color:#555555;\">라고 불리기도 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-56070a5d-845a-4056-8037-2efb735a870e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-56070a5d-845a-4056-8037-2efb735a870e\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDNfMTA3/MDAxNzU0MjE2NjExNzE1.rw9IyTQxQyt1u4RCepyOU24jx_7ql3Ps6sqMlOvcGd8g.Ly4wskTOowOVZBU9HnLdnbWr1bk81_I1hS5GMrMJEYwg.PNG/%EB%9D%A0%EC%A7%80_%EC%83%81%EC%84%B8001.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"595\", \"originalHeight\" : \"595\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDNfMTA3/MDAxNzU0MjE2NjExNzE1.rw9IyTQxQyt1u4RCepyOU24jx_7ql3Ps6sqMlOvcGd8g.Ly4wskTOowOVZBU9HnLdnbWr1bk81_I1hS5GMrMJEYwg.PNG/%EB%9D%A0%EC%A7%80_%EC%83%81%EC%84%B8001.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-51d88c53-dd8f-4bbb-8770-3a9fab8e32c9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b9391eaf-72f5-4a35-a2d5-39acffaa8772\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1634c216-489f-4efa-991b-9c5d77ebd832\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위 이미지처럼 트레이(Tray)를 감싸고 홍보나 제품 정보를 알려주는 용으로 사용되는 띠지, 슬리브도 많이 제작되고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-79c696df-1c29-4fd0-a5a6-eff77f96d41b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-212f2a8b-dd05-405a-8ded-5245850da432\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f7458ea7-6eec-46be-a80a-943fbc8e097f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-96389aee-1450-4f5a-90f7-05682b60376c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 띠지에는 기본적으로 몇 줄의 오시를 넣어 꺾이는 부분을 잘 접도록 만들고 끝부분에는 접착으로 마무리하는 인쇄물입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-76861153-36c1-479e-a2f6-dfd499e7d9fa\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-76861153-36c1-479e-a2f6-dfd499e7d9fa\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDNfMjA3/MDAxNzU0MjE2NzQ3OTU5.c_DDC_h9hB_CG2DrnU-PDdI0IvqhQnkZuMBNrbL4Glgg.UeahLtId8bCfhcDK4owDBkouoQTWYjfItACZEL9X0isg.PNG/%EC%8A%AC%EB%A6%AC%EB%B8%8C_%EC%9A%A9%EA%B8%B01.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"4000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"3000\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDNfMjA3/MDAxNzU0MjE2NzQ3OTU5.c_DDC_h9hB_CG2DrnU-PDdI0IvqhQnkZuMBNrbL4Glgg.UeahLtId8bCfhcDK4owDBkouoQTWYjfItACZEL9X0isg.PNG/%EC%8A%AC%EB%A6%AC%EB%B8%8C_%EC%9A%A9%EA%B8%B01.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-78fcc987-bbea-4c4e-8f47-b48d5c94e3dc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-78fcc987-bbea-4c4e-8f47-b48d5c94e3dc\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDNfMjgw/MDAxNzU0MjE2ODEyODMx.nfi86l6zC65MujyIgDuX8Da0K0q7DlUnzD7_VO3aJEUg.Ge0E4zbndX2biXXkSraCl3Rt5Ce9FUJPHdSoriGCWeog.PNG/image.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"904\", \"originalHeight\" : \"848\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDNfMjgw/MDAxNzU0MjE2ODEyODMx.nfi86l6zC65MujyIgDuX8Da0K0q7DlUnzD7_VO3aJEUg.Ge0E4zbndX2biXXkSraCl3Rt5Ce9FUJPHdSoriGCWeog.PNG/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-55326d2c-e5a6-48a2-8081-b4aeb4ce8c3c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bfdf148b-45cb-4a1b-8faf-0fee948fe273\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-bfb015c1-f6e1-46c6-b8f0-4138743edb77\" style=\"\">기본 사양</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-42d434d4-558a-40a3-bab0-bba6865d1b4b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7cfc5ff9-3fb1-4074-a7cd-ca5e7e5ee68d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-86a35802-9595-4584-97b1-a58d61496755\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>종이</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d0ac149b-cf50-43d3-b8dc-85fc39b28f9c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-679a26b6-2574-47ba-840e-6e1928e32c8a\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-52cf9e6b-3822-4813-84bb-8e42225eb12d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1e2a1f2b-3563-4c57-bbfd-30c8603ba065\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이는 다양하게 모든 종이로 제작이 가능합니다. 가장 일반적인 아트지/스노우지에서 부터 최고급용지까지 다양하게 제작이 될 수 있습니다. 물론 원가에 포함되는 부자재일 수 있어 비싼 종이를 사용하지 않지만 용도나 상황에 따라 박인쇄나 형압등의 제작을 가미하기도 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3cf803f8-bc55-4f2f-9955-10f377e00756\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d3e699ec-e31b-48e3-be46-3444df072d72\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a045b631-d025-48ac-bd83-8ff47c9deac1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aa05b9c5-2e54-4992-a897-1278c62e1794\" style=\"color:#555555;\">요 근래에는 친환경 종이가 각광을 받고 있어 크라프트지나 FSC 인증 용지가 많이 사용됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2b1932b7-b311-4046-bef0-0d3901d88082\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-df64a69b-5d4f-48e8-b8b6-a48ee6839f06\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7e521654-b356-407d-85da-d1d64846a9e3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ecc0a481-4937-4418-8c92-4033670dc269\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><a class=\"se-link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\": \"SE-ecc0a481-4937-4418-8c92-4033670dc269\", \"link\": \"https://blog.naver.com/samwon_paper/223889585153\"}' data-linktype=\"text\" href=\"https://blog.naver.com/samwon_paper/223889585153\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.naver.com/samwon_paper/223889585153</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> \n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c28bd2c9-cec1-4b37-9ece-2da68e24775b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1817acb5-1131-4f2c-9191-e7d41c106333\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3b6bbc0b-72e6-49ef-8a9a-cdeb79feeb79\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e32b6c64-5dc9-46e8-87da-b25085272955\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>인쇄</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-600f6273-4a27-46f2-bd47-85306356fe9e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-89a4bc71-0311-468d-8599-2638bf6edefc\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9c1833ae-07ab-496b-a246-b13134180207\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-56ebbf5b-9ef8-4952-8731-0812bb6113ed\" style=\"color:#555555;\">기본적으로는 단면 인쇄가 기본입니다. 후면에 인쇄되는 경우는 거의 없습니다. 여기에 브랜드를 강조하기 위해 별색으로 진행되기도 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4ae53a39-6e1f-4617-8234-8ae4a3417cf3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-accd792e-07fe-4dbc-8bdb-c1907786e066\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5b29c40c-c78e-44aa-8144-95a166c13403\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-688e22d2-c2ba-4a93-bf8d-406c21500200\" style=\"color:#555555;\">인쇄에서 주의할 점은 소량 생산에서의 별색은 제약사항이 될 수 있다는 것입니다. 디지털 인쇄에서 별색 기능은 제한적입니다. 반드시 상담을 통해 확인하고 주문하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-97d7b4ff-5abe-41d9-8866-88ef1ae6ef70\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-160b0cad-12de-41e9-bd7d-94063d2ab5c8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1a9af2d7-6c82-4744-8ee6-9d6d3da44a3c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-dad287a4-737f-49ff-8da5-d28893bec90e\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>후공정</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-89da723e-7044-4740-a673-a337316d9eb7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ebf49555-519a-49c3-9227-6f246a37c239\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bda8cf24-4dfa-41a1-a38f-61637229c96a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c7b7a925-f8a0-48e1-a289-c7a74ac22a2d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">후공정은 기본적으로는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-58586015-4001-47e5-a493-517134bddd5d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>누름선(오시)</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f3a8ffb3-e532-4d79-97f5-fc8c51c5c568\" style=\"color:#555555;\">을 작업합니다. 오시를 넣고 트레이에 꺾이는 부분에 맞춰 잘 접히도록 제작합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b984e3bc-a82f-46a7-92d6-03cf54683ce6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-b984e3bc-a82f-46a7-92d6-03cf54683ce6\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDNfMTQ1/MDAxNzU0MjE3NDgyNDAy.Be3zvXyBtUuEUxopN6Q0IyjGtM5KOIBJvP_KPiRFFhIg.1fLIEOeh3rvvIkIG68YRkL48wWKIWOq2dGWxCjq-KMYg.PNG/image.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"997\", \"originalHeight\" : \"617\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDNfMTQ1/MDAxNzU0MjE3NDgyNDAy.Be3zvXyBtUuEUxopN6Q0IyjGtM5KOIBJvP_KPiRFFhIg.1fLIEOeh3rvvIkIG68YRkL48wWKIWOq2dGWxCjq-KMYg.PNG/image.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5cdeb649-88c9-48d6-b802-a990da07435f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ee889f02-413c-4c54-badc-8a764ffd8b55\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e05aa55a-552f-4597-a249-23c5eacde59c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>박인쇄</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-95338096-0423-4b59-8448-dad5b9cc6a9a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">나 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-198ef2ca-bf37-4cfc-a6af-306001d40e51\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>형압</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-98ba269e-bae3-4703-af25-3dfbc81fb82e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">등의 후공정을 추가하거나 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-350b7fdb-efe5-4d80-9784-b71df28cdef3\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>부분 코팅</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-31b78ca8-40a0-4f4c-9851-cc6c448ee465\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이나 전체 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-abb1e04f-f0ef-449c-9b1f-47495910e0bf\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>코팅</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b2e1abee-4308-40be-b645-7ebeed583475\" style=\"color:#555555;\">도 가능합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bff873b6-09dc-4181-a8d2-b935e8c17559\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-85c06b44-8227-4a51-9bb9-a0ae01b180f2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-659e719d-38f7-4280-a651-ec084f10f7be\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9b607a4b-aea5-4546-a660-014217cd7b86\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>수량</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8b6f5dad-e962-4412-b688-7cf0025f76bd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ddcb3553-bdf0-499b-8168-2b97193d9780\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ea1d9a64-4830-4810-a5b2-422b39fcb85f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a3521609-a0ef-43d4-ba05-482bcd647e82\" style=\"color:#555555;\">주문 수량은 디지털로 1장에서부터 출발합니다. 이건 샘플용입니다. 포장되는 트레이에 맞게 제작되는지를 확인하는 용입니다. 물론 다품종 소량으로 100개, 200개를 주문하기도 합니다. 친절히 수량에 대해서는 설명을 드리겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-30912ee2-4613-47ce-bf53-c36e1951e3bf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2aa52e2a-99ed-4570-aef1-ddc5bea55007\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8b4ddcd0-7dca-4bd6-8ec2-1d7cb7050c7f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-26c021a8-e9f7-4c7c-853b-470e7aec0bc7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">오프셋인쇄의 경우 기본적으로는 1,000개부터 진행됩니다. 이 정도의 수량이어야 개당 단가가 나옵니다. 반드시 참고하시고 진행하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-56db087a-39f1-4b9e-bc61-19888e28b689\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-264f5c67-179f-4e04-bce6-db887491996c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-101bbadd-1a6d-4ae3-a829-4f6962b4ff03\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5def98a3-cc84-4d22-ba74-1f77095035d7\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>납기</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-82ad7687-5859-4872-a81f-868d8a070367\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-df8f3260-0d90-4e62-92b6-f94d01522f46\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c5216991-cdb5-43df-9fdf-e94ea802381e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5c53303b-e239-4e35-ad9c-244035aaa815\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디지털은 1~3일 안에 제작됩니다. 하지만 오프셋 대량 인쇄는 후공정 유무에 따라 납기가 유동적입니다. 별다른 후공정이 없다면 3~5일입니다. 참고하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c41111ae-fd21-4249-b23c-f4cebebcf635\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-c41111ae-fd21-4249-b23c-f4cebebcf635\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDNfMTk4/MDAxNzU0MjE4NDg2NjM2.g_XJgj2F-138sWuwHLf-bT0_jPa6WUrjSkcdw_jkC6cg.zUeLHYR4wbQm9D-VUUeg7dn3QsvYdmF50iwRyYmv17Ig.PNG/%EB%9D%A0%EC%A7%80_%EC%83%81%EC%84%B8002.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"595\", \"originalHeight\" : \"595\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA4MDNfMTk4/MDAxNzU0MjE4NDg2NjM2.g_XJgj2F-138sWuwHLf-bT0_jPa6WUrjSkcdw_jkC6cg.zUeLHYR4wbQm9D-VUUeg7dn3QsvYdmF50iwRyYmv17Ig.PNG/%EB%9D%A0%EC%A7%80_%EC%83%81%EC%84%B8002.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-4a4fe56c-be4d-446a-a452-6f72113c4b37\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c7da9f20-3463-4170-a850-f644900a10f8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-1fa0f983-ef31-4755-8414-89416c2a585f\" style=\"\">주의 사항</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3f88d7e9-dfb7-4f3f-9490-0d7393ac87e8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0ea6aa7f-4a99-48a8-9296-27066a7d6b14\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1a07731e-fef0-4118-87ec-a018684531ce\" style=\"color:#555555;\">띠지를 만들 때 반드시 주의해야 할 점은 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6ac4a8d6-c9a4-4812-824a-e2a1745c5d6d\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\">트레이(Tray)에 딱 맞는 제품의 제작</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-82822c62-f1e2-4893-b62c-7111bc1a2c8a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다. 이 사이즈가 잘 맞지 않는다면 헐겁거나 끼워지지 않는 사고가 발생됩니다. 제작 시 트레이(Tray)를 꼭 보내주시기 바랍니다. 이 트레이를 받고 규격을 결정합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-34066e67-1818-4555-959b-eb6c122f600b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cf58a5e9-4af9-438e-abcb-dc2b62bb28c5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dc23a7d8-f1ac-48cc-bdad-574506be2f7f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9eb091cc-966e-4df3-a710-39dcff018a41\" style=\"color:#555555;\">제품을 빛이 나게 해주는 좋은 띠지는 디자인과 단가가 매우 중요합니다. 언제나 (주)파파스컴퍼니과 상의하십시오. 최선을 다해 상담해 드리겠습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223957501800#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
